title: IAA Tonight | Is Odell Beckham Jr. Headed to a Contender?
description: CBS Sports Josina Anderson jumps onboard to discuss all the latest in the NFL news, and if Odell Beckham Jr. will be heading back to the field soon. Is he close to signing with a team in contention. Plus, Super Bowl Champ and Seahawks great Cliff Avril chimes in on the Russell Wilson situation that's been brewing in Denver.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar Kelly, Brandon Marshall, Cliff Avril)
